Celebrating July 4th by release a new logo for @typicalnature 💥🌴
This has been my company I’ve been working on since I lived in a shed, slowly trying to build hoping I can get the support from you all to make it an actual team one day. 🙏🏽
I have high hopes for my brand, even if I got to live on the streets again, I can say at least I tried. ❤️
